---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title='Privacy Policy | The Palm Beach Broker' description='Privacy Policy for The Palm Beach Broker real estate services.'>
  <section class='bg-forest py-20'>
    <div class='max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8'>
      <p class='font-sans text-gold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-3'>Legal</p>
      <h1 class='font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white font-light leading-tight mb-6'>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class='w-16 h-px bg-gold mb-8'></div>
      <div class='space-y-8 font-sans text-white/80 leading-relaxed text-base'>
        <p>Last updated: March 2026. This Privacy Policy describes how THE DANIEYIS GROUP LLC collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our website or real estate services.</p>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class='font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3'>1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We may collect: your name, email address, phone number, property preferences, and any information you provide when contacting us or completing forms on our website.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class='font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3'>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to provide real estate services, respond to inquiries, send property alerts and marketing communications, and improve our website.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class='font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3'>3. Text Messages and Emails (SMS Opt-In)</h2>
          <p>By submitting your contact information, you agree to receive calls, emails, and text messages from THE DANIEYIS GROUP LLC related to real estate services. Message and data rates may apply. Message frequency may vary. You can opt out at any time by replying STOP to any text message or using the unsubscribe link in our emails.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class='font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3'>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
          <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share it with service providers who help us operate our business, or as required by law.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class='font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3'>5. Terms and Conditions - SMS Services</h2>
          <div class='space-y-4 pl-4 border-l-2 border-gold/30'>
            <div>
              <h3 class='font-serif text-lg text-gold font-light mb-2'>5.1 SMS Confirmation and Reminders</h3>
              <p>We use SMS to confirm appointments, send reminders, and notify clients of schedule updates or important changes related to real estate services.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class='font-serif text-lg text-gold font-light mb-2'>5.2 Cancellation of SMS Service</h3>
              <p>You can cancel the SMS service at any time. Just text "STOP". After you send the SMS message "STOP" to us, we will send you an SMS message to confirm that you have been unsubscribed. After this, you will no longer receive SMS messages from us. If you want to join again, just sign up as you did the first time, and we will start sending SMS messages to you again.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class='font-serif text-lg text-gold font-light mb-2'>5.3 Technical Support</h3>
              <p>If you are experiencing issues with the messaging program, you can reply with the keyword "HELP" for more assistance, or you can get help directly at <a href='mailto:yourpalmbeachbroker@gmail.com' class='text-gold hover:text-white transition-colors'>yourpalmbeachbroker@gmail.com</a>.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class='font-serif text-lg text-gold font-light mb-2'>5.4 Carrier Liability</h3>
              <p>Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class='font-serif text-lg text-gold font-light mb-2'>5.5 Message and Data Rates</h3>
              <p>As always, message and data rates may apply for any messages sent to you from us and to us from you. Message frequency may vary. If you have any questions about your text plan or data plan, it is best to contact your wireless provider.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class='font-serif text-lg text-gold font-light mb-2'>5.6 Privacy Questions</h3>
              <p>If you have any questions regarding privacy, please read our privacy policy or contact us at <a href='mailto:yourpalmbeachbroker@gmail.com' class='text-gold hover:text-white transition-colors'>yourpalmbeachbroker@gmail.com</a>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class='font-serif text-2xl text-gold font-light mb-3'>6. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class='font-sans text-white/80 leading-relaxed text-base'>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at <a href='mailto:yourpalmbeachbroker@gmail.com' class='text-gold hover:text-white transition-colors'>yourpalmbeachbroker@gmail.com</a> or call <a href='tel:+17869758002' class='text-gold hover:text-white transition-colors'>+1 (786) 975-8002</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
